  SCENARIO 1 — DB fails on node1
  ────────────────────────────────
  galera1 DOWN
       │
       ▼
  HAProxy health check fails for galera1
       │
       ▼
  All DB traffic routes to galera2
       │
       ▼
  Both CS management nodes continue via VIP ✓

  SCENARIO 2 — Management fails on node1
  ────────────────────────────────────────
  cs-mgmt1 DOWN
       │
       ▼
  HAProxy HTTP check fails for cs-mgmt1
       │
       ▼
  All UI traffic routes to cs-mgmt2
       │
       ▼
  Portal remains accessible ✓

  SCENARIO 3 — Node1 completely down
  ────────────────────────────────────
  node1 DOWN (DB + Management + Keepalived)
       │
       ▼
  Keepalived VRRP detects master failure (~2s)
       │
       ▼
  VIP moves to node2
       │
       ▼
  HAProxy on node2 serves all traffic
       │
       ▼
  CloudStack accessible — session re-login required ✓


